h","LLM call order: ZAI(glm-5) вҶ’ NOUS вҶ’ OPENROUTER, all via `call_llm()`","Prompt minimization rule: system prompt + context must be minimal tokens","KST-based market hours: trading 09:00-15:30, closing, pre-market","Both `server.py` (local) and `api/index.py` (Vercel Flask) must have identical changes","Frontend index display shows only change rate (%) to avoid line breaks","Chatbot uses server cache data instead of search; search is disabled","Work approval required from user before code modifications","No hallucination rule: no stock price predictions, data-only basis, no inference output","AI answers must be specific: cite technical indicator values, 3-5 paragraphs","Conversation filter: only `role == \"assistant\"` items passed to AI in `chat_with_ai()`","Stock fee deduction: sellAmount Г— 0.215% (fee 0.015% + tax 0.20%); fields `sellFee`, `realizedProfit`, `realizedProfitRate`","Architecture: lightweight-charts@4.1.3 with Naver Finance `siseJson.naver` API; `/api/chart?code=` endpoint","Dual server: `server.py` (port 8090, Python HTTP) and `api/index.py` (Vercel serverless, Flask)","LLM fallback chain: ZAI вҶ’ NOUS (`stepfun/step-3.7-flash:free`) вҶ’ OpenRouter (`nex-n2-pro:free` вҶ’ `gpt-oss-120b:free`)","Env vars: `OPENROUTER_KEY`, `ZAI_KEY` stored as Vercel env vars","в–Ів–ј symbol system for change rate display instead of +/-","Server-side news filtering: 24-hour window using `cutoff = time.time() - 86400`","TradingView free widget does NOT support KRX symbols","Naver Finance API returns Python list syntax (single quotes), parse with `ast.literal_eval()`","lightweight-charts v4.1.3: `createChart()` вҶ’ `addCandlestickSeries()`; unversioned CDN may load v5+ with breaking API changes","Korean candlestick colors: Up (м–‘лҙү) = red `#ef5350`, Down (мқҢлҙү) = teal `#26a69a`"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/projects/c7d56d4e-4055-47be-ae32-d050be5aa949/MEMORY.md"],"id":"obs_mr9t8x2p_ee2a3d230516","importance":10,"narrative":"Loaded the durable project memory for the Korean stock market dashboard. This defines the project requirements, strict operational rules (LLM call order, prompt minimization, approval workflow), and critical technical constraints. Any code changes must account for the dual-server architecture and mirrored endpoints.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Persistent project knowledge including architecture, rules, and constraints","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:47:33.743Z","title":"Read project MEMORY.md for stock-dashboard","type":"file_read"},"obs_mr9t8x5c_d25441099876":{"concepts":["session notes","scratchpad","checkpoint reconciliation","memory management"],"confidence":1,"facts":["File located at /home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md","File contains only header/template content (2 lines total)","Title: \"# Session notes\"","Purpose: \"Free-form scratchpad for the main agent\"","Entry format: `## [turn N В· YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ]` (minute precision UTC)","Checkpoint writer reconciles entries at checkpoint events","Instruction to scan for duplicates before appending"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md"],"id":"obs_mr9t8x5c_d25441099876","importance":2,"narrative":"Read the initial session notes file which serves as a template/header for agent scratchpad entries. The file is currently empty with only formatting instructions. This establishes the convention for how future entries should be structured with turn numbers and UTC timestamps.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Examined structure of scratchpad notes file","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:47:33.838Z","title":"Read session notes template file","type":"file_read"},"obs_mr9t8x64_954fe2eabe3d":{"concepts":["workflow step hook"],"confidence":0.9,"facts":["Timestamp: 2026-07-06T22:47:33.866Z","Hook type: step_finish"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9t8x64_954fe2eabe3d","importance":1,