al AI assistant"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Technical signal logic inserts reasons based on tech_score (15+ threshold) and ai_signal conflict resolution","US market indices defined: лӢӨмҡ°мЎҙмҠӨ (DJI@DJI), S&amp;P 500 (SPI@SPX), лӮҳмҠӨлӢҘ (NAS@IXIC), н•„лқјлҚён”јм•„ л°ҳлҸ„мІҙ (SOX@SOX)","Chat message limit set to CHAT_MSG_LIMIT = 20","generate_us_market_analysis() uses LLM with regex JSON extraction for market summary and highlights","Fallback functions _fallback_highlights() and _fallback_summary() provide Korean-language defaults","Cache key includes _date field for daily invalidation"],"files":["/home/rg3270/blog/stock-dashboard/server.py"],"id":"obs_mr9t92kn_0d5735f7fbf7","importance":6,"narrative":"Read a section of the stock dashboard backend containing technical signal scoring logic, US market AI chat infrastructure, and LLM-based market analysis generation. The code implements a scoring threshold system for buy/sell/hold signals with reason tracking, and a separate US market analysis module that fetches indices and news to generate Korean-language summaries via LLM with regex-based JSON parsing. This reveals the hybrid approach of AI-powered analysis with rule-based fallbacks.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Reading lines 1304-1803 of server.py","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:47:40.868Z","title":"Stock dashboard server.py US market AI analysis code","type":"file_read"},"obs_mr9t94sm_55c1ab454599":{"concepts":["LLM context engineering","chat history persistence","technical indicator integration","Korean financial labeling","stock dashboard"],"confidence":1,"facts":["save_chat_history() persists chat history to CHAT_HISTORY_FILE (globally cached + JSON)","build_chat_context() assembles portfolio summary, news articles, holdings, and technical indicators","Technical indicators included: RSI(14) with status thresholds, MACD momentum, Bollinger Band position%, Stochastic","Signal scale: strong_buy/buy/hold/sell/strong_sell mapped to Korean labels (к°•л Ҙл§ӨмҲҳ/л§ӨмҲҳ/кҙҖл§қ/л§ӨлҸ„/к°•л Ҙл§ӨлҸ„)","News context limited to top 10 items, 2 articles per stock","RSI thresholds: &gt;70 кіјл§ӨмҲҳ, &gt;60 к°•м„ё, &lt;40 м•Ҫм„ё, &lt;30 кіјл§ӨлҸ„"],"files":["/home/rg3270/blog/stock-dashboard/server.py"],"id":"obs_mr9t94sm_55c1ab454599","importance":6,"narrative":"The server builds enriched context for an AI stock chat assistant by combining portfolio summary (value/profit/rate), recent news per ticker, holdings details, and real-time technical analysis (RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, Stochastic). Technical signals are aggregated into a composite score mapped to Korean buy/sell recommendations. This context is passed to the LLM for conversational investment insights.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"AI chat feature constructs context from portfolio, news, and indicators","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:47:43.748Z","title":"Chat context building with technical analysis in stock dashboard","type":"file_read"},"obs_mr9t94uv_29eb3d1031e8":{"concepts":["task management","task listing"],"confidence":0.9,"facts":["Task list operation completed with zero tasks"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9t94uv_29eb3d1031e8","importance":1,"narrative":"A task listing command was executed which returned no active tasks. This indicates an empty task queue or that all previous tasks have been completed.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Task list query completed successfully","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:47:43.830Z","title":"List tasks returned no results","type":"command_run"},"obs_mr9t977a_76b9cad315d3":{"concepts":["Korean stock market trading hours","KST timezone handling","Market phase detection","RAG context building","Stock dashboard backend"],"confidence":1,"facts":["search_web function is disabled (returns empty list)","get_market_status determines current KST trading phase","Korea market phases: н”„лҰ¬л§Ҳмј“ 08:00-08:50, л©”мқёл§Ҳмј“ 09:00-15:20, мӢңк°ҖлӢЁмқјк°Җ 15:30-15:40, м• н”„н„°л§Ҳмј“ 15:40-20:00","Weekends return \"нҒҙлЎңмҰҲ(мЈјл§җ)\" status","get_next_trading_day excludes weekends","chat_with_ai builds context with portfolio, news, US/KR market data","Korean weekday labels: мӣ”, нҷ”, мҲҳ, лӘ©, кёҲ, нҶ , мқј"],"files":["/home/rg3270/blog/stock-dashboard/server.py"],"id":"obs_mr9t977a_76b9cad315d3","importance":6,"narrative":"The file contains core functions for a stock dashboard backend that manages Korean stock market status checks and AI chat interactions. The get_market_status function maps times to trading phases with appropriate кұ°лһҳ мғҒнғң messages. The chat_with_ai function aggregates portfolio, news, US market, and Korean market contexts before sending to an AI model, with capability to highlight news for specifically mentioned stocks in user queries.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Reading functions related to market trading hours and AI chat context building","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:47:46.864Z","title":"Korean Stock Dashboard Market Status Functions","type":"file_read"},"obs_mr9t97em_e2e6c869e61e":{"concepts":["Flask API","Upstash Redis REST","AI provider aggregation","Naver Finance API","Korean stock market","API key management","in-memory caching"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Flask app initialized with static_folder=None","Data files: data.json, chat_history.json, us_market.json","Upstash Redis REST API used via kv_get/kv_set helper functions","Hardcoded ZAI_KEY present at line 81","KRX_API_KEY has default value at line 83","Multiple AI providers configured: ZAI, NOUS, OpenRouter, OpenCode","Naver realtime finance polling URL defined for Korean stock data","AI cache with 300s TTL using in-memory dict","History tracking with deque (MAX_HISTORY=12)"],"files":["/home/rg3270/blog/stock-dashboard/api/index.py"],"id":"obs_mr9t97em_e2e6c869e61e","importance":5,"narrative":"Read the first 100 lines of the stock dashboard Flask API. The file configures multiple LLM providers, Korean stock data sources via Naver, and Redis caching. Hardcoded API keys were observed, indicating a security concern for credential management.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Initial page of Python Flask backend with Redis and AI integrations","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:47:47.132Z","title":"Read Flask stock dashboard API config","type":"file_read"},"obs_mr9t9jz6_bca4e39dbb2a":{"concepts":["LLM fallback chain","environment variable configuration","Vercel deployment","API key management","server-side chat debugging"],"confidence":1,"facts":["File written successfully to /home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/checkpoint.md","User reported Korean dashboard chat AI failing with \"мқјмӢңм Ғмқё л¬ём ң\" error on stock market query","call_llm() fallback chain (server.py:2161-2206) exhausted all providers: OpenCode, ZAI, NOUS, OpenRouter","Environment variables OPENCODE_KEY, ZAI_KEY, OPENROUTER_KEY potentially unset on local server","Vercel api/index.py has ZAI_KEY hardcoded at line 81 while server.py reads from environment","LLM call order: OpenCode GLM-5.2 вҶ’ ZAI GLM-5 вҶ’ NOUS (3 models) вҶ’ OpenRouter (2 models)"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/checkpoint.md","server.py","api/index.py","app.js"],"id":"obs_mr9t9jz6_bca4e39dbb2a","importance":7,"narrative":"A comprehensive session checkpoint was written documenting the debugging state of a Korean stock dashboard chat feature. The AI consistently returns a fallback error message indicating all LLM providers in the chain have failed. Key investigation points identified include missing environment variables on the local server, potential instability of free NOUS models, and the discrepancy between local and Vercel API key configuration.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Documented LLM fallback chain failure analysis","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:48:03.424Z","title":"Session checkpoint for chat AI debugging","type":"file_write"},"obs_mr9t9mcb_91b19e6b31d8":{"concepts":["stock portfolio","drag-and-drop persistence","Vercel serverless","Upstash Redis","Korean stock API (KIS)","HTML5 Drag and Drop API","frontend state management","portfolio holdings"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Multiple memory entries dated 2026-07-06 from portfolio project (c7d56d4e)","Drag-and-drop reordering implemented with HTML5 Drag and Drop API, PUT /api/reorder endpoint","Portfolio updated: мӮјм„ұм „кё°(009150) 1мЈј@1,795,000мӣҗ, SKмҠӨнҖҳм–ҙ(402340) 2мЈј@1,492,000мӣҗ м¶”к°Җ","save_config() Vercel bug: file write fails on read-only FS preventing kv_set() to Upstash Redis","Drag order restoration bug: server-side fix insufficient, frontend lacks local state causing 1-2s reset via loadPortfolio() re-render","Proposed fixes: frontend localStorage for order, or reorder exception handling in save_config()","Foreigner/institutional trading section hidden pending KIS API integration","Referenced commits: c0770f6, c17ae12, 8fd557a, 9bb1536","Holdings: нҳ„лҢҖм°Ё 25мЈј@499,600, мӮјм„ұм „мһҗ 30мЈј@300,250, мӮјм„ұм „кё° 1мЈј@1,795,000, SKмҠӨнҖҳм–ҙ 2мЈј@1,492,000"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/projects/c7d56d4e-4055-47be-ae32-d050be5aa949/MEMORY.md"],"id":"obs_mr9t9mcb_91b19e6b31d8","importance":5,"narrative":"Read the final portion of MEMORY.md documenting 2026-07-06 work on a Korean stock portfolio app. Key issues include an unsolved drag-and-drop order persistence bug on Vercel caused by read-only filesystem preventing Redis sync, and frontend state management gaps that reset user-defined ordering within seconds after page load or cache invalidation.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Korean stock portfolio project notes from 2026-07-06","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:48:06.488Z","title":"Memory entries - drag-drop bugs and portfolio updates","type":"file_read"},"obs_mr9t9tpi_c7c2c1cf1b31":{"concepts":["LLM provider fallback","environment variable configuration","Vercel deployment","API key management","frontend state management"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Documented chat AI fallback message when all LLM providers fail (call_llm at server.py:2206)","ZAI_KEY is hardcoded in api/index.py:81 but read from environment variable in server.py:35","Vercel deployment uses the hardcoded ZAI_KEY from api/index.py","OPENCODE_KEY and OPENROUTER_KEY are only read from environment variables","Drag order restoration bug remains unresolved due to frontend state management absence"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/projects/c7d56d4e-4055-47be-ae32-d050be5aa949/MEMORY.md"],"id":"obs_mr9t9tpi_c7c2c1cf1b31","importance":6,"narrative":"The agent documented critical debugging findings in the project memory file. Two key issues were recorded: (1) a fallback message behavior when all LLM providers fail, which helps diagnose AI service outages, and (2) an architecture inconsistency where ZAI_KEY is hardcoded in the API layer but managed via environment variables in the server layer, affecting Vercel deployment behavior. These findings are essential for understanding AI service reliability and credential management.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Added findings about LLM fallback behavior and API key configuration inconsistency","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:48:16.035Z","title":"Update project memory with AI fallback and ZAI_KEY findings","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mr9t9y3y_0218e970ea74":{"concepts":["LLM provider fallback","environment variable configuration","hardcoded API keys","session notes"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Korean AI chat service returned fallback message: \"мЈ„мҶЎн•©лӢҲлӢӨ. нҳ„мһ¬ AI м„ңл№„мҠӨм—җ мқјмӢңм Ғмқё л¬ём ңк°Җ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ\"","User query was about domestic stock market (\"мҳӨлҠҳ көӯлӮҙмҰқмӢң м–ҙл–Ёкұ° к°ҷм•„?\")","call_llm() fallback message was triggered","All LLM providers failed","api/index.py hardcodes ZAI_KEY","server.py uses environment variables","Unset OPENCODE_KEY/OPENROUTER_KEY causes providers to be skipped"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md"],"id":"obs_mr9t9y3y_0218e970ea74","importance":6,"narrative":"Session notes were appended to document an active debugging session where the Korean AI chat service returned a fallback error instead of answering a stock market query. The entry captures analysis indicating all LLM providers failed, with configuration discrepancies including a hardcoded ZAI_KEY in api/index.py versus env-var usage in server.py, and missing OPENCODE_KEY/OPENROUTER_KEY preventing providers from being used.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Korean AI chat returned fallback error on stock market query","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:48:21.740Z","title":"Write session notes documenting LLM provider failure","type":"file_write"},"obs_mr9taiox_7d0d1ad0788e":{"concepts":["LLM provider fallback chain","environment variable configuration","Vercel serverless functions","dual server architecture","free LLM model instability"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Checkpoint written to /home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/checkpoint.md","call_llm() at server.py:2161-2206 returns fallback message when all LLM providers fail","LLM provider chain: OpenCode GLM-5.2 вҶ’ ZAI GLM-5 вҶ’ NOUS (3 models) вҶ’ OpenRouter (2 models)","Missing environment variables: OPENCODE_KEY, ZAI_KEY, OPENROUTER_KEY default to empty string in server.py","api/index.py has ZAI_KEY hardcoded at line 81 (Vercel), server.py uses env var","NOUS free models (stepfun/step-3.7-flash) are unstable with service outages/rate limits"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/checkpoint.md","server.py","api/index.py","app.js"],"id":"obs_mr9taiox_7d0d1ad0788e","importance":7,"narrative":"Saved a comprehensive session checkpoint documenting the debugging of a Korean stock dashboard chat AI that returns \"мЈ„мҶЎн•©лӢҲлӢӨ. нҳ„мһ¬ AI м„ңл№„мҠӨм—җ мқјмӢңм Ғмқё л¬ём ңк°Җ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ\" for all queries. The root cause area is identified as call_llm() failing across all LLM provider fallbacks, with missing environment variables and unstable free NOUS models as likely culprits. Next step is to check server logs for actual error messages and verify Vercel environment variable configuration.","sessionId":"ses_0c6628e6effeQsZet8mPljFykJ","subtitle":"Korean stock dashboard chat AI returning fallback message due to all LLM providers failing","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:48:48.414Z","title":"Dashboard chat AI debugging checkpoint saved","type":"file_write"}}␀␀Ҡ ␀ф—яя